<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.3">
<l>tantaiyun tāyumuṟ ṟāruniṟkat taṉivaḻi pōyiṉā ḷeṉṉuñcollu</l>
<l>vantapiṉ ṉaippaḻi kāpparitu māyavaṉ vanturuk kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>kontaḷa mākkip parakkaḻittuk kuṟumpucey vāṉōr makaṉaippeṟṟa</l>
<l>nantakō pālaṉ kaṭaittalaikkē naḷḷiruṭ kaṇeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Once the words “She has gone down a path on her own</l>
<l rend="indent">When [her] father, mother, and relatives were there!” have come out,</l>
<l>It is hard to stop slander. The Marvellous [Lord] has come and shown Himself!</l>
<l>Send me in the dense darkness to the outer gate of [the mansion] of Nandagopāla</l>
<l>Who begot a son who does mischief by creating turmoil and causing disgrace.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
